snippet.title: VELOCITY NOODLE ►Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Master the art of lightning-fast noodle delivery in VELOCITY NOODLE! With deadly traps, and a range of moves to master, unleash your inner speed-runner and take in the sights of a fast-paced neon city. Are you ready to become the ultimate noodle delivery master? 

VELOCITY NOODLE is out now on for $12.99!
